== Welcome to GrandCentralCP (development version)

GrandCentralCP is a light web server control panel written in Ruby on Rails

Right now the development version can perform the following tasks:

- Creation of MySQL databases
- Configuration of Apache2
- Creation of customers as admin


== Getting Started

1. Apache2 Setup -> "apt-get install apache2"
2. MySQL Setup   -> "apt-get install mysql-server mysql"
3. Ruby Setup    -> "apt-get install ruby"


== Basic Usage

When you start webrick the interface is available on http://localhost:3000/ on your server.


